<I c="Tutorial" i="tutorial" m="tutorials.tutorial" n="tutorial_EP16_World" s="393819">
  <T n="category">368974<!--tutorial_EP16_category_Rendezvous--></T>
  <T n="name">0xD3B0E886<!--Welcome to Ciudad Enamorada--></T>
  <L n="slides">
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP16\UI\Tutorial\EP16_World_LessonSlide1.png">2f7d0004:00000000:dedbb9391fd690c5</T>
      <T n="text">0x461F4C88<!--Welcome to Ciudad Enamorada, where romance flourishes, and the heart grows fonder. This colorful city embodies love, with plenty of places to bond with your special someone. How about adding something extra to your date? Try out local cuisine at the food stalls throughout the city, or purchase something nice for your sweetheart at Isabela’s Flower Shops. From date spots for couples to bustling hot spots full of eligible singles, Ciudad Enamorada provides anything one might need to lose oneself in passion and timeless memories.--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP16\UI\Tutorial\EP16_World_LessonSlide2.png">2f7d0004:00000000:dedbb9391fd690c6</T>
      <T n="text">0xC2A06435<!--Not everyone wants to live the nightlife. Some would like to settle down, and Vista Hermosa is perfect for easy-going couples to set up a home with their family. Couples can write their name on the <b>Wall of Love</b>, hoping for a lifetime of happiness. Visit <b>Laguna del Abrazo</b> for a drink and a good time, or maybe stop at the <b>Beso Rápido Motel</b> across the street for something more intimate...a good night’s rest.--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP16\UI\Tutorial\EP16_World_LessonSlide3.png">2f7d0004:00000000:dedbb9391fd690c7</T>
      <T n="text">0xC8AB2E36<!--Plaza Mariposa is the beautiful picturesque central square nestled within the bustling city of Ciudad Enamorada and provides an enchanting backdrop for a sunset stroll with the love of your life. <b>Media Naranja</b> is a park that offers perfect spots for a moment of tranquility over delicious drinks while you gaze at the luscious greenery around you. The local cuisine at the food stalls or the charming gifts from Isabela’s Flower Shop will only add to the romantic atmosphere. For those from out of town, the vacation rental <b>Villa Cálida</b> is ready for you and your beloved to visit and experience the city for yourself. Don’t forget to make a wish at the <b>Fountain of Dreams!</b>--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InEP16\UI\Tutorial\EP16_World_LessonSlide4.png">2f7d0004:00000000:dedbb9391fd690c0</T>
      <T n="text">0x9C5AD197<!--Rebuilt and modernized, Nuevo Corazón is the pinnacle of Ciudad Enamorada nightlife. Immerse yourself in the sultry ambiance and discover potential paramours at <b>Mirador del Amor</b>, a nightclub for those looking for mystery and allure. After a night of energetic dancing, recharge and build your stamina at <b>SUDOR</b>, a gym where you can train your endurance and maybe even find a new workout partner.--></T>
    </U>
  </L>
